      • sendPayment

        public com.google.common.util.concurrent.ListenableFuture<RouterOuterClass.PaymentResponse> sendPayment(RouterOuterClass.PaymentRequest request)
        
SendPayment attempts to route a payment described by the passed
PaymentRequest to the final destination. If we are unable to route the
payment, or cannot find a route that satisfies the constraints in the
PaymentRequest, then an error will be returned. Otherwise, the payment
pre-image, along with the final route will be returned.

      • estimateRouteFee

        public com.google.common.util.concurrent.ListenableFuture<RouterOuterClass.RouteFeeResponse> estimateRouteFee(RouterOuterClass.RouteFeeRequest request)
        
EstimateRouteFee allows callers to obtain a lower bound w.r.t how much it
may cost to send an HTLC to the target end destination.
